184.77.text:
In teaching and managing writers, David Broder 
said it best: &quot;Good journalists are skeptical of 
their sources and of their own biases.&quot;

194.13.text:
And so, in class and management, I always try 
to say, &quot;Be aware of yourself.  Listen to 
yourself.&quot;

